---
title: Asian-Glazed Tofu & Veggie Buddha Bowl with Avocado & Peanuts
description: There’s so much to choose from, where should we start! The roasted pumpkin looks so vibrant, but the stir-fry glaze on the tofu
is making everyone’s mouth water. A refreshing pickled cucumber, avocado chunks or the sesame slaw could be a relaxing way
to start, not to mention the coconutty sweet chilli mayo! Let’s have it all!
